snippet.title: Laadla (1994) Full Hindi Movie (4K) Sridevi & Anil Kapoor & Raveena | Farida Jalal | Bollywood Movie
snippet.description:
Laadla is a 1994 Indian Bollywood action drama film, directed by Raj Kanwar and produced by Nitin Manmohan. The film stars Anil Kapoor, Sridevi, and Raveena Tandon in pivotal roles. And Farida Jalal, Aruna Irani, Anupam Kher, Prem Chopra, Paresh Rawal, Mohnish Behl, Shakti Kapoor, Alok Nath, Arun Bakshi others in supportive role. It is known for its strong dialogues, emotional story and powerful performances.

The story revolves around Raju (Anil Kapoor), a hardworking and principled man who is hired by a ruthless and arrogant factory owner, Sheetal (Sridevi). Their personalities clash due to their different ideologies. Raju believes in honesty and humanity, while Sheetal believes in power and control. Their constant conflict leads to unexpected developments, including a dramatic marriage twist that changes their lives.

Romeoâ€¯S3, directed by Guddu Dhanoa and produced by Penâ€¯Studios and Wildâ€¯Riverâ€¯Pictures, is an adrenaline-fueled Hindi action thriller set in the underworld of Goa.
Thakurâ€¯Anoopâ€¯Singh stars as DCP Sangramâ€¯Singhâ€¯Shekhawat, a fearless cop who goes undercover to dismantle a dangerous drug cartel while uncovering a sinister virus-linked conspiracy.
Opposing him is Palakâ€¯Tiwariâ€™s investigative journalist, Tanu, whose dogged pursuit of truth pulls her into Sangramâ€™s high-stakes mission.
Packed with explosive fight scenes, high-speed chases, and larger-than-life stunts, the film delivers classic masala action in a bold, cinematic.
While praised for its sheer energy and punchy performances, critics note the storyline sometimes leans on predictable tropes and formulaic twists.

Ni gabhru rakaane bebe bapu ji to baahre na
Na saade kolo vaade hone lagne ve laare na
Ni tere kolo main vi tere maa-pe charwaune na
Te mere kolo ranjhe wangu pashu jaane chaare na
Na dil to greeb bhave bhute na ameer ni
Aa jehde nal bhai kathi kri na mandeer ni
Ni susti na nede tede mitran de laggdi 
Ni 24 ghante lor vich rehnda ae sareer ni
Ni bhaiyan te yakeen security jeyo z te
Ho bade dil lutte akh mittraa di red ne
Ho dabb nal lgga jo rakaane 30 bore da
Flower bna dewe bhaida eh forehead te
Na nimm jehe lot aune mitthi teri talk to
Na pighluga dil eh jwaani teri hot to
Dass fer sher da ni rutba ki reh gya
Je oh vi gya pattya rakaane cat walk to
Oh zindgi nu reejha nal maande aa baithke
Koi chakkr ni meeru bai khada jado back te
Ho asi befikre 9 10 vje sojiye
Ni sathon gallan adhi raat honiya ni chat te
Ni chattya ni kde v yaara ne billo thukk ke
Oh jo vi kita shar-e-aam kreya ni lukk ke
Oh Kayi saale raula pake kehn asi ki aa
Te sara kujh dssya ae mittra di chupp ne
Jo tappde aa salya nu shittra di ghaat ni
Oh fer vekhi baith jaane sara chupp chaap ni
Ohh kehnde ne ke saade naalo vadda koi vaily ni
Te Dhaai saah ne ch*** de utte bhora maas ni
Neet saaf rabb ne vi kujh ni lakoya kude
Tension ni len koi dinda bai saroya kude
Dhannwaad karda va saareya da dil to
Haaye pauna si punjab kattha lentar te hoya kude
Ho dunia ta jitti baitha hun kithe haar da
Jhool jhool ture kude pota jagtar da
Oh jihna hun takk aukh vich hi aa kattli
Ni maapeya nu geda mai lwauna ik bahar da
Ho guru ghar jaake bhala sareyaa da mangda
Ho adhi cho vi adhi cheej doojeya na vand da
Ho mai ni kehnda rabb bahla deyi jawe menu
Jinna mera banda onna hi ohto mangda

Van life is very common in western countries. So in this channel at E Bull Jet, we are featuring van life in India. This channel will showcase the real-life in India and nearby countries.

We would like to bring our Van life though this channel - E BULL JET

Get ready for a rollercoaster of emotions with Biwi No.1 (1999), a delightful comedy directed by David Dhawan. This film features an ensemble cast including Salman Khan, Karisma Kapoor, Sushmita Sen, Anil Kapoor, and Tabu, delivering a perfect blend of humor and drama.

The story revolves around Prem (Salman Khan), a wealthy man leading a blissful life with his wife Pooja (Karisma Kapoor) and their two children. Their idyllic existence is disrupted when Prem becomes infatuated with Rupali (Sushmita Sen), a glamorous model. As Prem's extramarital affair unfolds, Pooja discovers the betrayal and, with the help of her supportive family and friends, devises a plan to win back her husband and restore her family's happiness. The narrative explores themes of love, trust, and the importance of family bonds, all wrapped in a comedic package. 

Biwi No.1 was both a critical and commercial success, becoming the second highest-grossing Hindi film of 1999. The film received several accolades, with Sushmita Sen winning the Filmfare Award for Best Supporting Actress for her portrayal of Rupali. The movie's soundtrack, composed by Anu Malik, also contributed to its widespread popularity. 

Experience the laughter, tears, and ultimate redemption in Biwi No.1 (1999)!

snippet.title: Every Worker Needs to Know This! | ESIC | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
The Employeesâ€™ State Insurance Corporation (ESIC) is a government-run social security and health insurance scheme designed to protect Indian workers. Under the ESI Act, 1948, it provides financial and medical benefits to employees and their families in times of sickness, maternity, disability, or death due to employment injury.
This video explains how the scheme works and the key benefits you should know about.
âœ… Medical Benefits â€“ Free treatment for employees and their dependents
âœ… Sickness Benefit â€“ 70% of wages during certified medical leave
âœ… Maternity Benefit â€“ Paid leave for pregnant women
âœ… Disablement Benefit â€“ Financial aid in case of injury at work
âœ… Dependantsâ€™ Benefit â€“ Monthly pension for the family in case of death
âœ… Funeral Expenses â€“ One-time payment for funeral costs
âœ… Vocational Rehabilitation â€“ Support for disabled employees to regain employment
Whether you're an employee or employer, this is a must-watch to understand your rights and responsibilities under ESIC.

âœ… Dependantsâ€™ Benefit â€“ Monthly pension for the family in case of death
âœ… Funeral Expenses â€“ One-time payment for funeral costs
âœ… Vocational Rehabilitation â€“ Support for disabled employees to regain employment

snippet.title: Mortal Kombat II | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
It's called Mortal Kombat (II).
Mortal Kombat II â€“ only in theaters and @imax October 24. #MortalKombatMovie #FilmedForIMAX 

From New Line Cinema comes the latest high-stakes installment in the blockbuster video game franchise in all its brutal glory, Mortal Kombat II.  This time, the fan favorite championsâ€”now joined by Johnny Cage himselfâ€”are pitted against one another in the ultimate, no-holds barred, gory battle to defeat the dark rule of Shao Kahn that threatens the very existence of the Earthrealm and its defenders.

Karl Urban stars as Johnny Cage, alongside Adeline Rudolph, Jessica McNamee, Josh Lawson, Ludi Lin, Mehcad Brooks, Tati Gabrielle, Lewis Tan, Damon Herriman, with Chin Han, Tadanobu Asano as Lord Raiden, Joe Taslim as Bi-Han, and Hiroyuki Sanada as Hanzo Hasashi and Scorpion.

Director Simon McQuoid returns to helm the follow up to his explosive 2021 cinematic adventure, from a screenplay by Jeremy Slater, based on the videogame created by Ed Boon and John Tobias.  The film is produced by Todd Garner, James Wan, Toby Emmerich, E. Bennett Walsh and McQuoid, and executive produced by Michael Clear, Judson Scott, Slater and Lawrence Kasanoff.  

Joining McQuoid behind the camera are director of photography Stephen F. Windon, production designer Yohei Taneda, editor Stuart Levy and costume designer Cappi Ireland, with casting by Rich Delia and music by Benjamin Wallfisch.

New Line Cinema Presents an Atomic Monster/Broken Road Production, a Fireside Films Production, Mortal Kombat II.  The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, only in theaters and IMAXÂ® across North America on October 24, 2025, and internationally beginning 22 October 2025.

snippet.title: UK & Europe Trains Are Not What I Expected | Unscripted StandUp Comedy "Rant" by Rahul Dua | 2025
snippet.description:
Coming to 14 cities across UK & Europe in Sept'25 with my comedy special Allow Me! Tickets: https://linktr.ee/therahulduatour

Germany ka train system + UK ki train strike = Confused Indian traveler ka breakdown ğŸ˜…. 
In this unrehearsed, unscripted, straight-from-the-heart stand-up bit, I talk about my chaotic Europe tour in 2023 - from Berlin to Munich, Birmingham to London - and how desi expectations just don't match European transport â€œefficiencyâ€. ğŸ˜¤ I don't think I'd use "punctuality" and "German trains" in the same sentence again :P

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Farm Tour in Tamil | Steffi Ulagam
snippet.description:
In this vlog, we visited a farm in which we had planted some fruit trees a couple of years ago when we visited India. Those plants have grown up and have started producing fruits. While there are predominantly coconut trees, we were able to get some other fruit trees between them. Join us as we explore our small farm in India, enjoying the fruits of our labor with a delightful fruit harvest. We're picking mangoes, coconuts, and dragon fruit, savoring the taste of these homegrown fruits. 

I hope seeing these fruit trees kindled some desire in you for gardening and I hope you will also try to grow some plants. Hope you liked this week's vlog and see you next week with more interesting videos.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Mr. Truth | Episode 11 | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
This is a reflection of a disturbing reality unfolding in our land. In recent times, our own people have watched silently, and in some cases, even enabled,  the rise of certain outsiders who have crossed every line of decency, safety, and respect.
Based on true incidents reported in our state, on how some non-locals, once welcomed as workers and settlers, have now turned aggressive, entitled, and even violent â€” involved in molestation, assault, and intimidation of local men and women. The worst part? A few local gundas and power-hungry individuals are protecting them for money and personal benefit.
This video is not against any community and does not target or generalize all non-locals but it raises a serious question, How long will we stay silent when dignity, safety, and respect are at stake? So this is against those who abuse the hospitality and silence of the land they live in. Itâ€™s against those who disrespect our mothers, threaten our youth, and treat the locals as second-class in their own homeland.
Not all are bad, but ignoring the bad ones is dangerous.
Letâ€™s not protect criminals. 
Letâ€™s protect our community. Lets save our land.

nl-NL.title: Nu verandert het pad van de moesson! De regen stopt in centraal India, de moesson keert terug naa...
nl-NL.description:
Vanaf 18 juli neemt de regenval in Madhya Pradesh en Bihar af. Op 19 juli wordt zeer lichte regen verwacht in Bihar, Jharkhand, Uttar Pradesh, Madhya Pradesh, Punjab, Haryana en Delhi, inclusief Noord-Rajasthan. Maar op 19 juli vormt zich een cyclonische circulatie in de noordwestelijke Golf van Bengalen. Door de gevolgen hiervan zal het opnieuw regenen in de oostelijke districten van West-Bengalen, Odisha en Bihar. Deze regenval zal zich opnieuw richting Centraal-India verplaatsen en de moesson activeren. Zware regenval houdt aan in de bergen. Ook in Kerala wordt zware regenval verwacht en aan de kust van Karnataka matige tot zware regenval. In Maharashtra, inclusief Mumbai, zal de regenval wat milder worden.

it.title: Ora il percorso del monsone sta cambiando! La pioggia cesserÃ  nell'India centrale, il monsone tor...
it.description:
Dal 18 luglio, le precipitazioni inizieranno a diminuire in Madhya Pradesh e Bihar. Il 19 luglio, sono previste piogge molto deboli in Bihar, Jharkhand, Uttar Pradesh, Madhya Pradesh, Punjab, Haryana e Delhi, incluso il Rajasthan settentrionale. Tuttavia, il 19 luglio, si formerÃ  una circolazione ciclonica nel Golfo del Bengala nord-occidentale. A causa del suo effetto, le piogge ricominceranno a cadere nei distretti orientali del Bengala Occidentale, dell'Odisha e del Bihar. Questa attivitÃ  piovosa si dirigerÃ  nuovamente verso l'India centrale, innescando il monsone. Le forti piogge continueranno sulle montagne. Sono previste forti piogge anche in Kerala e piogge da moderate a intense sulla costa del Karnataka. Le piogge diventeranno piuttosto deboli nel Maharashtra, inclusa Mumbai. #Monsoon2025 #Monsoon #AggiornamentiMeteo #PrevisioniMeteo #SkymetWeather #Skymet #Meteo

id.title: Kini arah Monsun berubah! Hujan akan berhenti di India tengah, Monsun akan kembali ke timur | Cua...
id.description:
Mulai 18 Juli, aktivitas hujan akan mulai berkurang di Madhya Pradesh dan Bihar. Pada 19 Juli, hujan ringan diperkirakan terjadi di Bihar, Jharkhand, Uttar Pradesh, Madhya Pradesh, Punjab, Haryana, dan Delhi, termasuk Rajasthan utara. Namun, pada 19 Juli, sirkulasi siklon akan terbentuk di Teluk Benggala Barat Laut. Akibat pengaruhnya, hujan akan kembali turun di wilayah timur Benggala Barat, Odisha, dan Bihar. Aktivitas hujan ini akan kembali menuju India tengah dan mengaktifkan monsun. Hujan deras akan terus berlanjut di pegunungan. Hujan deras juga diperkirakan terjadi di Kerala dan hujan sedang hingga lebat di pesisir Karnataka. Hujan akan sedikit lebih ringan di Maharashtra, termasuk Mumbai.

#Monsun2025 #Monsun #PembaruanCuaca #PrakiraanCuaca #CuacaSkymet #Skymet #Cuaca

snippet.title: Mere Murshid Mere Yaara | Sarzameen | Prithviraj S, Kajol, Ibrahim Ali Khan, Vishal Mishra, Jaani
snippet.description:
Mere Murshid Mere Yaara is a heartfelt qawwali-inspired love song, beautifully sung by Vishal Mishra and Salman Ali.

Releasing July 25, only on JioHotstar!  

ğŸ‘‰ Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Credits:
Song: Mere Murshid Mere Yaara  
Album: Sarzameen
Singer: Vishal Mishra, Salman Ali
Music Director: Vishal Mishra
Lyricist: Jaani
Featuring Starcast: Kajol, Prithviraj Sukumaran, Ibrahim Ali Khan

Music Arranged & Produced by: Vishal Mishra
Music Assistants: Kumar Gaurav Singh, Trihangku Lahkar, Bitupon Boruah
Recorded, Mixed & Mastered by: Vijay Dayal @ YRF Studio
Special Thanks: Azeem Dayani
Strokes: Tapas Roy
Guitar & Bass: Rhythm Shaw
Keys & Harmonium: Vishal Mishra
Chorus / Qawali: Vivek Naik, Sagar Lele, Umesh Joshi, Santosh Bote, Mangesh Shirke, Mohan Morajkar, Anil Bhilare, Yashad Ghanekar, Siddhant Karawde, Karan Kaagle, Vidit Patankar
Live Rhythms Arranged by: Prashant Sonagra, Swaranjay Dhumal
Tabla: Prashant Sonagra & Navin Sharma
Dholak: Swaranjay Dhumal, Navin Sharma, Ishtiyaq Khan, Mushtaq Khan
Ghungroo Tabla: Shankar Kamble
Percussion: Swaranjay Dhumal, Prashant Sonagra

Lyrics:
Yaaron Ka yaar Haiâ€¦. 
Madadgar Parwardigaaraâ€¦ 
Mere Yaar Nu Sajdaaa Karke.. 
Ohde Naam di Eid Guzaraaaâ€¦..

Tum mile ho iss tarah se 
Jaise Maula mil gaya ho 
Mile Badal Mili Nadiyaan 
Mila Sukoonâ€¦

Meri Aankhon ke rasto se 
Bann gaya saans tu meri Aur phir 
Saanso se hoke 
Bann gaya khoon..

Dil ka Dariya Chalkeeeeâ€¦ 
Rab Hai Aaya chal kee..
Tu Dariya Hai Mai hoon 
Saahil Tera Hoga na..

Mere Murshid Mere Yaara 
Tu Chann Mai Tuteya Taara 
Mere peer ka tu hai Ishara 
Bakhudaaâ€¦ Bakhudaa..

Mere Murshid Mere Yaara 
Tu Chann Main Tuteya Taara 
Mere Ali ka tu hai Ishara 
Bakhudaaâ€¦ Bakhudaa..

Re Ga Ga Ga.. Re Ga Ga Ga.. 
Re Ga Ga .. Re Ga Ga.. Re Ga.. 
Re Ga Ga Ga.. Re Ga Ga Ga.. 
Re Ga Ma Pa.. Ma Ga Re Sa..

Dha Sa Sa Sa.. Dha Sa Sa Sa.. 
Dha Sa Sa.. Dha Sa Sa.. Dha Sa 
Dha Sa Sa Sa.. Dha Sa Sa Sa.. 
Dha Sa Re Ga Re Sa Dha Pa..

Aaa..Aaaâ€¦
 
Kitne he Baandhein Hai 
Dhaage re Mazaro Pe.. 
Mere liye tune
Yeh toh bata..

Apne Liye Tune.. 
Kuch Nahi Manga Hai
Mere liye Maangi Har dua 
Meri Maut thi aayi Ishq Mere
Meri Jaan bachayi Ishq Tere

Meri Khaatir Tune Teri Meri 
Khaatir Tune Teri 
Khushiyon Ko Hai Maara.

Mere Murshid Mere Yaara 
Tu Chann Mai Tuteya Taara 
Mere peer ka tu hai Ishara 
Bakhudaaâ€¦ Bakhudaa..

Main Ik nadi sa haan
Ik Nadi Sa Tu Hain Naseeb ka Jharna

Tere Gale se Lag ke O sai 
Pairon pe tere hai marna 
Tujh Ko Meri ho jo Aarzoo 
Toh Dauda Chala Aau main. 
Itni Dua na kar iss tarah
Ki Rab Khud na bann jau mai

Ab kya kahu ke mere Huzoor 
Har Har Nafaz mai bas tu hai
Meri Arzoo mai.. meri bandagi mai.. 
Bas tu hai.. tu hai..bas tu hai

Iss Ishq ki na Intehaan
Ab kya kahu ki mere huzoor
 
Tu Dariya hai Mai hoon Paani 
Tu Dariya hai Mai hoon Paani 
Dariya ka hoon Maaraâ€¦

Mere Murshid Mere Yaara 
Tu Chann Mai Tuteya Taara 
Mere peer ka tu hai Ishara 
Bakhudaaâ€¦ Bakhudaa..

Mere Murshid Mere Yaara 
Tu Chann Main Tuteya Taara 
Mere Peer ka tu hai Ishara 
Bakhudaaâ€¦ Bakhudaa..

Amman is the South Indian Goddess of Rain. She is the main South Indian mother/goddess in the southern India. Mari is closely associated with the Hindu goddess Parvati and Durga. 
Her festivals are held during the late summer/early autumn season of Aadi throughout Tamil Nadu and Deccan region, the largest being Aadi Thiruvizha. Devotees offer Pongal that is cooked using earthen pots which are made during the festive season. Rituals such as fire walking and mouth or nose piercing are also practised. Mari in Tamil means rain. Thus she is referred to as Mariyayee or Aathaa. Aathaa means mother or grandmother. She symbolizes sacrifice, motherhood, abundant wealth and good health. 

May Goddess Amman Bless You All ! Om Sakthi !

snippet.description:
#AadiVarugutheaAmma #AmmanSongs #Veeramanidasan #LREswari #mahanadhishobana #shakthishanmugaraja 

The album " Aadi Varuguthea Amma - à®†à®Ÿà®¿ à®µà®°à¯à®•à¯à®¤à¯‡ à®…à®®à¯à®®à®¾ " is dedicated to Goddess Amman. This album has 9 songs sung by L.R Eswari, Shakthi Shanmugaraja, Veeramanidasan, Mahanadhi Shobana, P. Susheela, S Janaki, Bombay Saradha, Sakthi Dasan  
Lyrics By : Mugilan, Bharathi Ganesh & Shakthi Shanmugaraja
Music By : Kanmani Raja, D.V.Ramani & Shakthi Shanmugaraja
Produced By : Unique Recording

Amman is the South Indian Goddess of Rain. She is the main South Indian mother/goddess in the southern India. Mari is closely associated with the Hindu goddess Parvati and Durga. 
Her festivals are held during the late summer/early autumn season of Aadi throughout Tamil Nadu and Deccan region, the largest being Aadi Thiruvizha. Devotees offer Pongal that is cooked using earthen pots which are made during the festive season. Rituals such as fire walking and mouth or nose piercing are also practised. Mari in Tamil means rain. Thus she is referred to as Mariyayee or Aathaa. Aathaa means mother or grandmother. She symbolizes sacrifice, motherhood, abundant wealth and good health. 

May Goddess Amman Bless You All ! Om Sakthi !

snippet.title: Teri Galiyon Mein (Official Video) Javed-Mohsin | Mohammad Faiz | Sanika Bhoite | Danish Sabri
snippet.description:
Mohabbat bhi wahi. Galti bhi wahi aur tabaahi bhi.

Get ready to feel every beat of heartbreak with the official video of â€œTeri Galiyon Meinâ€ â€“ a soulful tale of love, loss, and longing.

Sung by the sensational Mohammad Faiz, composed by the hitmaker duo Javed-Mohsin, and penned by the lyrical genius Danish Sabri â€“ this oneâ€™s going to stay with you long after it ends.

Featuring the stunning Sanika Bhoite, the video narrates a a story that will tug at your heart strings. 

#TeriGaliyonMein #MohammadFaiz

Featuring the stunning Sanika Bhoite. 

ğŸ§  Audio Credits

âŸ Music composer : Javed-Mohsin
âŸ Singer : Mohammad Faiz 
âŸ Sufi  vocals by - Danish sabri 
âŸ Lyrics by - Danish sabri 

âŸ Music team :

âŸ Original soundtrack theme written and composed by : Javed-Mohsin 

âŸ Music produced by : Jackie Vanjari
âŸ All live guitars played by : Shomu seal 
âŸ Solo  violin played by : Jitender Thakur 
âŸ Live sarangi played by : Muddasar Ali khan 
âŸ Indian rhythm ( Tabla & dholak ) by : Raju Sardar and team , firoz khan , sanjeev sen , Zuber hussain Warsi , Tahir Hasan
âŸ Percussions and side rhythm played by : Satyajit Jamsandekar
âŸ Live strings played by : Prakash verma , Sunil Verma , Jitender Jawda , Shyam jawda , Prabhat kishore , sandeep thakur , dilip Bose , Mahendra Bedi , chandan singh , raju padhiyar , dilip Bose 
âŸ Live strokes played by : Tapas Roy
âŸ Solo Trumpet played by : Kishore Soda 
âŸ Backup qawali vocals by - Sameer khan royal , Aman khan , Harshad Munir & khalid Iqbal 
âŸ Song recorded @Studio 504 by : Rahul M sharma 
âŸ Javed-Mohsinâ€™s legal advisor : Rohini Vakil 
âŸ Assistant Mix engineer - Michael Edwin Pillai 
âŸ Mixed & Mastered by : Eric Pillai @FSOB

ğŸ¬ Video Credits

âŸ Director - Sneha Shetty Kohli 
âŸ Starring - Sanika Bhoite & Mohammad Faiz
âŸ DOP - Girish Kant
âŸ Line producer - Karan Dedhia 
âŸ 1st Ad - Amitesh Sanghani
âŸ Assistant director - Celestine Dcruz
âŸ Assistant Costume Stylist - Neha Khub & Dhwani
âŸ Associate Dop - Akshay Sarode
âŸ Choregrapher - Jayshree Kelkar
âŸ Assistant Choreographer -Shwetha j Poojary
âŸ Gimbal Opretor -Sumit jaiswal 
âŸ Associate Gimbal Operator-Sunny jaiswal 
âŸ Costume stylist -Vibhuti Chamaria
âŸ Production designer - Rupendra Das 
âŸ Hair &Make up - Amit Pawar Diwakar Kadam
âŸ Location - Swagat Villa by the pool
âŸ Editor - Bunty Nagi
âŸ Editing studio - Just Right Studioz
âŸ DI - DreamTone Studio
âŸ DI Colorist - Prashant B Dhotre
âŸ DI Producer - Alpa Thakkar
âŸ Casting (Sanika Bhoite) - Ashish Natekar (Big Wave Entertainment)
âŸ Faiz hair - Azruddin

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Lyrics:

Mukhda :

Raas na aaya mujhko tujhse dil lagana
Hasti hai yeh duniya mujhko kehke deweena
Yaad rakhega ek din saara yeh zamana
Aankhon mein aansu lekar mera muskurana

Hai mere paas wahi jo gaya hai tu de kar

Teri galiyon mein phir raha hoon toota dil lekar
Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa kehkar
Teri galiyon mein phir raha hoon toota dil lekar
Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa kehkar

Antra :
Yeh maanta hoon ishq se badhkar koi jaadu tona nahi
Jise tu khel ke tod de yeh dil hai khilona nahi

Yeh maanta hoon ishq se badhkar koi jaadu tona nahi
Jise tu khel ke tod de yeh dil hai khilona nahi

Duayein de rahe hain tujhko saare gham seh kar

Teri galiyon mein phir raha hoon toota dil le kar
Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa keh kar
Teri galiyon mein phir raha hoon toota dil le kar
Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa keh kar

Outro :
Dhoondhne walon ko tu bata de mera pata hai teri galiyon mein
Dard mein dooba dil hai magar jeene ka mazza hai teri galiyon mein

Main hoon woh bejaan mohabaat jiski dawa hai teri galiyon mein
Duniya hai mandir masjid mein mera khuda hai teri galiyon mein

Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa keh kar

Bewafa keh kar
Bewafa keh kar
